comment: A red-haired girl is jumping in the air with a skateboard near her feet .

comment: Man breakdancing while trying to push himself off the ground , while his legs are in the air and hands and head on the floor .

comment: Two workers in reflective vests are taking a break and sitting down .

comment: Girl on a street using a hula hoop , with three people in the background .

comment: An elderly gentleman displays that he still has n't lost his knowledge of how to operate , with just a couple of horses and an old plow , free of automation .

comment: Two men wearing traditional Finnish clothing dance while a woman , also wearing traditional Finnish clothing , watches and claps for them .

comment: Three guys in military clothing dig a hole in the desert with shovels .

comment: A man in a military uniform is sitting at a desk speaking into a walkie-talkie .

comment: A man wearing army camouflage stands behind the steering wheel of the vehicle he is operating .

comment: A skydiver hangs from the undercarriage of an airplane or some sort of air gliding device .

comment: A guitarist performs during a concert along with his band mate , on bass guitar .

comment: A family of three stands in their kitchen helping each other get the dishes done .

comment: A woman running in a purple shirt pushes a stroller with her child in it on a sidewalk with neatly cut grass on either side .

comment: A foreign person walks with a material down a walkway heading through a residential area of a foreign country that is not recognizable through the photo .

comment: Three men smile at the camera surrounded by a pile of green and yellow fruits .

comment: A man in a black and yellow outfit has just kicked a soccer ball , with another player watching in the background .

comment: A man with a white shirt , breakdances in front of a crowd of young boys .

comment: A man on stage in the act of jumping , with a little boy in the background really enjoying it .

comment: A young boy is falls to the awkwardly to the ground with a surprised look on his face while a group of people watch from behind .

comment: A man works on a kitchen appliance , while in the foreground are various ingredients - an orange , three eggs , self-rising flour and butter .

comment: A firefighter climbs a ladder towards a building that is on fire ; smoke is everywhere .

comment: Two soccer players in blue facing away from each other , as one walks away and the other crouches facing the goal .

comment: A little school age boy in a green shirt is making a face at the camera in front of ten other children .

comment: A boy playing soccer goes for a header as his opponents look on from the bench .

comment: A soccer player in a red outfit is about to kick the ball while a player wearing a blue outfit looks at him while running in the background .

comment: A white lady in water with brown hair behind a orange surfboard .

comment: A young man in a black hat and white t-shirt is suspended in their air on his skateboard .

comment: a racing car is making a wide turn on the dirt track and there is a lot of dust in back of him
Translated Comment: уралдааны машин Шороон зам дээр өргөн эргэлт хийж, түүний ар талд маш их тоосонцор байдаг

comment: A car throws up a large amount of dust and rocks as it races by spectators .

comment: One white car is speeding down a dirt road , throwing dirt up into the air behind it as it goes by .

comment: The man attempting an extreme stunt on his bicycle is wearing a black helmet and black elbow pads .

comment: A rowing team member in a black and purple uniform is carrying his boat to the water while another team member is carrying the oars and another watches .

comment: A baseball pitcher wearing a purple and white uniform throwing a baseball from the mound .

comment: Two little boys in swim trunks are sitting on a log at the edge of a body of water .

comment: Man playing for a baseball team with a blue protective hat and baseball uniform , playing for South Carolina , is swinging the bat and missing the ball .

comment: A man in a helmet and protective gear driving a go kart , numbered 65 , on a narrow paved road .

comment: a surfer in a dark wetsuit carries a white surfboard towards the ocean .

comment: This boy , dressed in colorful knit clothing , seems to need a handkerchief .

comment: Four men in multicolored running clothes and shoes sprinting down a street while onlookers watch .

comment: A man is sitting on a blue stool working outside at a worn wooden desk .

comment: A young boy with a blue and gray shirt is making designs on a beach in the sand with a wooded area behind him .

comment: A man with glasses holding an infant dressed in a white jumper .

comment: A man with glasses is playing his instrument in a small crown of people that includes another man in a suit with a trumpet .

comment: A woman in a brown peace t-shirt grilling vegetables on a large gas grill .
Translated Comment: Том хийн махан шар махан шарлагын газар ногод шарсан энгэрэнгүй

comment: A person with their hair in a ponytail washing dishes in front of the window with the blinds closed .

comment: A man wearing a red garment is hunched over another man who has fallen and is rolling on the grass while other people are in visible in the background .

comment: A man sitting on railroad tracks eating something and selling something displayed on top of a crate .

comment: A construction worker is standing on a crane placing a large arm on top of a stature in progress .

comment: An American football punter is just about to kick the ball to the receiving team with the rest of his team running behind him .

comment: A man wearing a blue shirt is dribbling a soccer ball while a man in a white shirt is trying to take it .

comment: Three men with blue jerseys try to score a goal in soccer against the other team in white jerseys and their goalie in green .

comment: An overweight man , wearing a blue and white soccer uniform , is playing soccer and there is a red circle drawn on the grass near where he is standing .

comment: A man in white and black riding gear jumps his motorbike high above the ground with blurry field and clouds in the background .

comment: A young woman in white pants , boots , and an olive green coat passes by a market while a street musician plays electric guitar behind her .

comment: At what appears to be a rodeo , a man tackles an animal to the ground while being watched by a dozen people .

comment: A young boy about the age of 2 sits on gray rocks while holding something small in his hand .

comment: Three men are standing in a dark market with bright red and yellow goods .

comment: A baseball player getting ready to throw a pitch in his windup .

comment: A little boy digs a trench on the beach while a little girl carries a Minnie Mouse bucket from the water .

comment: A boy using a shovel to dig sand with the ocean in the background .

comment: Three individuals are working with tools at a table lit by a florescent lamp .

comment: A young man in a blue jersey riding a yellow dirt bike appears to be riding it around a corner in the midst of a race .

comment: An old man in white garb is sitting next to a stone wall and shaping a piece of metal with a hammer .

comment: A guitarist , a drummer , and another band member are performing on stage with red lights on the background .

comment: The lead singer visited with his band members and had the guitarist sing along with the song .

comment: Two men on fast motorcycle speeding around a corner on a racetrack .

comment: A young pale woman 's face with short blond-hair , and electric blue eyes , with a cherry coming out of each of her nostrils .

comment: A man in a black wetsuit rides a wave with his dog on the surfboard .

comment: a group pf railway construction workers fixing a section of railroad track .

comment: Two girls , one dressed in a salmon colored shirt , the other dressed in red shirt , are dancing on a roof .

comment: young gentlemen wearing green shorts is walking towards the ocean with his surfboard
Translated Comment: Ногоон шорт өмссөн залуу ноён нь далайн тавцан дээр далайгаар алхаж байна

comment: A white horse and a rider wearing a ale blue shirt , white pants , and a black helmet are jumping a hurdle .

comment: A jockey on a horse jumping over two hurdles at once in the middle of a dirt field

comment: A horse back rider wearing white breeches , black tall boots , and spurs jumping a large oxen in a jumpers course on a gray horse with splint boots .

comment: A woman with a red shirt and blue boots wearing a plastic bag to protect her from the rain glances down at her bundle of bok choi vegetables .

comment: A man with brown hair and a brown jacket playing the trumpet at a concert .

comment: Two archaeologists are examining something in their dig site .

comment: A man on a bicycle , wearing cycle gear , riding at a fast past down paved trail surrounded by tree 's and grass .

comment: Two people dressed in their bicycle attire racing against each other or in a marathon race , racing on pavement .

comment: A girl in a white tank top posing with a guitar in front of a red Chevelle .

comment: A little boy is holding a lit sparkler in the backyard .

comment: A blue-colored racing sailboat sporting the number 5 and Oracle corporate logos is sailing just off a rocky beach with a grass-covered sloping hill .

comment: A sailboat splashing in the water as some people look over the deck .

Translated Comment: Хөгшин, сахалтай хүн дэлгүүрийн цонхны фонт дээр гартаа хотын гудамжинд гараа барьж байхдаа жижиг металл шүгэл тоглодог.

comment: Six men are sitting in a small boat in the water apparently moored to an unseen dock .
Translated Comment: Зургаан эрчүүд нэг жижиг завин дээр сууж байгаа нь үл үзэгдэх док руу аялсан нь харагдаж байна.

comment: On a beautiful sunny day , this young man is performing the sport called waterskiing .
Translated Comment: Сайхан нартай өдөр, энэ залуу нь Waterskiing гэж нэрлэгддэг спортоор хичээллэж байна.

comment: A young girl in an orange shirt holds a small white flower up to her face .
Translated Comment: Улбар шар өнгийн цамц өмссөн залуу охин нь жижиг цагаан цэцэгийг нүүр рүү нь барьдаг.

comment: A man is bending over , aiming a shot with a pool cue on a billiard table .
Translated Comment: Эрэгтэй хүн сууж, усан сантай хамт усан сантай хамт усан сантай хамт буудсан.

comment: A bicycle racer has an energized look on his face while being closely escorted by another vehicle .
Translated Comment: Унадаг дугуй унаж буй унаачин нь өөр тээврийн хэрэгслээр ойртож байхдаа нүүрэн дээрээ эрч хүчээр эрч хүчтэй харагддаг.

comment: A saxo bank bicyclist racer is on the road , on his bike peddling , with his arms on the center of his handlebar .
Translated Comment: Саку Банкны дугуйн уралдаан зам дээр явж, дугуйны дөрөө дээр гараа барьсан самбар дээр гараараа гараа сунгаж байна.

comment: A girl playing soccer in a green field with some trees in the background .
Translated Comment: Ногоон талбайд хөл бөмбөг тоглож байсан охин.

comment: A baseball player up to bat wearing a white uniform with a red baseball helmet , hoping for a hit to get him to first base at least .
Translated Comment: Улаан бейсболын тоглогчдод цагаан өнгийн жигд хувцас өмссөн улаан бейсболын малгай өмссөн цагаан жигд хувцас өмсөж, ядаж эхлээд цохихыг хүсч байна.

comment: People shopping as well as a man in the background who appears to be a business owner of the fruit stand .
Translated Comment: Хүмүүс жимс, түүнчлэн жимс, жимсний байрны эзний бизнес эрхэлдэг хүн юм.

comment: A shirtless man wearing a cross necklace walks away from a brown brick building , with a chainsaw in the background .
Translated Comment: Хөндлөн зүүлт зүүсэн цамцгүй эр нь хүрэн тоосгон барилга дээрээс хол зайд алхдаг.

comment: A blond female dressed in a revealing outfit is throwing white shirts into the crowd with her brunette coworker several feet behind her .
Translated Comment: Илүү шаргал үстэй эмэгтэй хувцас өмссөн хувцас өмссөн хувцас өмссөн хувцас нь цагаан цамцныхаа цэлмэг цамц руу хэдэн хөлөө цайруулж байна.

comment: A team of young volleyball players saying a pep talk right before a big game .
Translated Comment: Залуу волейболын тоглогчдын баг том тоглолтын өмнө зөв тоглодог.

comment: Red car number 96 driving down a dirt road by the tree line kicking up dust in its trail .
Translated Comment: Улаан автомашины дугаар 96 нь модны шугам нь модны шугамыг мөрөн дээр нь өшиглөдөг шороон замаар явдаг.

comment: A older man appears to be at a party sitting on a purple bench and he is wearing blue jeans a black leather jacket and white socks .
Translated Comment: Настай хүн ягаан вандан сандал дээр сууж, цэнхэр жинсэн өмд өмсөж, цэнхэр жинсэн өмд өмссөн цэнхэр жинсэн өмд өмсдөг.

comment: A worker dressed in orange overall sprays off an ocean side road with high pressure water .
Translated Comment: Улбар шар өнгийн хувцас өмссөн ажилчин өндөр даралттай усаар далайн эрэг дээр цацдаг.

comment: One climber is sitting on the rock overlooking the ocean whilst another climber is on her way up .
Translated Comment: Нэг уулчин өөр уулберыг үл тоомсорлож буй далай дээр сууж байна.

comment: A barefoot boy and girl facing each other stand on a sidewalk dressed in jeans and blue t-shirts at the park .
Translated Comment: Хөл нүцгэн хөвгүүн, эмэгтэй хүний явган хүний зам дээр бие биенийхээ явган хүний зам, цэцэрлэгт хүрээлэнд байрладаг явган хүний зам дээр зогсож байв.

comment: Five cyclists , all wearing the same uniforms , are riding one behind the other in a bicycle race .
Translated Comment: Таван дугуйчид, бүгд ижил дүрэмт хувцас өмссөн, дугуй унадаг дугуй унаж буй зүйлсийн ард нэг хүн унаж байна.

comment: A motorcycle races along a deserted road where there are trees in the background .
Translated Comment: Ариун цэврийн мод байдаг цөлийн дагуух мотоцикль уралддаг.

comment: A girl with long hair and a microphone stands in front of a crowd of people .
Translated Comment: Урт үстэй охин, микрофон, микрофон олон хүмүүсийн урд зогсож байна.

comment: A woman wearing a bright red shirt and a yellow jacket is ladling something into a metal pan while surrounded by fresh produce at an outdoor market .
Translated Comment: Тод улаан цамц өмссөн эмэгтэй, шар хүрэм нь гадаа зах зээл дээр шинэхэн саваар хүрээлэгдсэн байдаг.

comment: Vendors at an Asian outdoor market , selling giant mushrooms under red umbrellas .
Translated Comment: Азийн гадаа зах зээл дээрх борлуулагч, улаан цэврүүтний аварга том мөөг зарах.
